---
name: generate_feed_rewrites
description: >
  Generate AI-powered Merchant Center title and description rewrites using
  FeedGen + Gemini. Three targeting styles: (1) Pass `productIds` to rewrite
  specific SKUs the user named. (2) Pass `mode='underperformer'` (the default)
  to auto-pick the SKUs with the worst ROAS / CTR / spend-without-conversions
  — use this for prompts like "rewrite the bottom 20 products by ROAS" or "fix
  our money-losing listings". (3) Pass `mode='stale'` for tenants with no ads
  data yet (picks high-price SKUs that have never been rewritten). Every
  rewrite lands in `product_feedgen_rewrites` as `pending` and must be
  approved through the existing Approval Queue before it ships to Merchant
  Center. Returns per-product rewritten title, description, qualityScore
  (0-100), and reasoning.
---
Rewrites always land in the Approval Queue first — never claim a rewrite has
shipped to Merchant Center.
